query: SELECT id, DATE_FORMAT(date, '%Y-%m-%d') as date_str, cash, network, total, (CAST(cash AS DECIMAL(10,2)) + CAST(network AS DECIMAL(10,2))) as calculated, (CAST(total AS DECIMAL(10,2)) - (CAST(cash AS DECIMAL(10,2)) + CAST(network AS DECIMAL(10,2)))) as diff FROM dailyRevenues WHERE branchId = 1 AND (CAST(total AS DECIMAL(10,2)) - (CAST(cash AS DECIMAL(10,2)) + CAST(network AS DECIMAL(10,2)))) != 0
